        "eprint_url": "https://arxiv.org/pdf/2508.12021v1",
        "pub_url": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2508.12021v1",
        "snippet": "Unsupervised federated learning (UFL) has gained attention as a privacy-preserving, decentralized machine learning approach that eliminates the need for labor-intensive data labeling. However, UFL fac",
